Name: Orc Massage
About the game: You're just an innocent and celibate Orc moving to the big city in order to start a new life. Earn money and increase your abilities so you can be the best Masseur around! VIP clients are the worst of the bunch... The stress they face in their daily lives brings them to you! Get to learn your clients wants and needs so that you can effortless take care of any pains they may have! Be careful though! Doing a good job may lead to some... consequences. You wouldn't want to destroy that nice image of yourself... right?
